perform even if only one person was in the audience 
its ok it keeps you tempered rivers said after friday 
nights myrtle beach show youre just that much more grateful 
next weekend when you go back to bigger houses every time the limo 
pulls up its nice to know they can take it away from you too 
rivers who also performed to a small audience in charleston on 
