additional troops and equipment were expected tuesday afternoon 
with most of the remainder arriving wednesday 
the pentagon said last week that it decided on the buildup 
because of the instability of the current situation in panama 
the heavyhanded tactics of noriega in dealing with the situation 
and the potential for increased threats to us citizens and 
interests 
