two members of president reagans cabinet and 
four members of congress have written letters of support for lyn 
nofziger to the judge who will sentence the former presidential 
aide for illegal lobbying 
the letters from energy secretary john s herrington and labor 
secretary ann mclaughlin were among 62 from current and former 
government officials that were filed monday with a defense memo 
that urged nofziger serve a period of unsupervised probation 
letters also were sent by sen chic hecht rnev reps jack 
kemp rny helen delich bentley rmd mervyn dymally 
dcalif exsen paul laxalt rnev and former health and human 
