commemoration organized by italys tiny maverick radical party 
some of the demonstrators carried banners with kings picture 
and others carried multilingual posters calling for an end to 
racial discrimination worldwide a solution to the palestinian 
issue and the drawing together of nations in a united states of 
europe 
